trans-unit.source: Refactorings
trans-unit.target: Refactorings

trans-unit.source: With IntelliCode, you never need to miss a code refactoring location again.
trans-unit.target: With IntelliCode, you never need to miss a code refactoring location again.

trans-unit.source: It locally tracks your edits, detects when you are performing a repetitive action, and offers to apply that same action in other places you may need to do so.
trans-unit.target: It locally tracks your edits, detects when you are performing a repetitive action, and offers to apply that same action in other places you may need to do so.

trans-unit.source: For instance, if you are refactoring, and have missed locations where that refactoring could be applied, it will help you find those locations and fix them.
trans-unit.target: For instance, if you are refactoring, and have missed locations where that refactoring could be applied, it will help you find those locations and fix them.

trans-unit.source: https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/intellicode-refactorings-3.png
trans-unit.target: https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/intellicode-refactorings-3.png

trans-unit.source: IntelliCode is aware of the semantic structure of your code.
trans-unit.target: IntelliCode is aware of the semantic structure of your code.

trans-unit.source: This semantic awareness detects cases where the variable names in your refactorings are different but the essential structure of the change is the same:
trans-unit.target: This semantic awareness detects cases where the variable names in your refactorings are different but the essential structure of the change is the same:

trans-unit.source: If you don’t like a suggested refactoring you can select the ignore option on the lightbulb, and we won’t bother you about that detected pattern again unless you recreate it.
trans-unit.target: If you don’t like a suggested refactoring you can select the ignore option on the lightbulb, and we won’t bother you about that detected pattern again unless you recreate it.
